使韩国扩大 Mirae 审查范围"&gt;当地监管机构的审查&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;这一事件凸显了即使是最平常的沟通障碍也可能对从事数十亿美元交易的金融家产生重大影响。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 24px;" /&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;委内瑞拉的两次地震已&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/gT8iy4LBos6lH25nqiu3sV9yRWmJ8dKsCxeUeGp9U3C1MuPkEDoUeicqjwx_Yga3Xfw-OK80lst_gYmGSqOQ9cR2ZupY6AYtp3FA9CEJivWcswBJw7CYELC1l9g0CBKroD8aPSqTSeMU2CN5WMjR9LXzItpIR2LfHOMOCksQj-UEbgP7nUhoVKFjgiXSwZ-jPUWvdweQwSKfonduPl1oHbqno4OEs6hAyklha4lpi8RoP_HdTHvBgrD7PGUyAzzlCsjsgCufTvcnNPvqzJ8RAnM251zhHR3NyqanLC6-q-m4COV4jnHRqRTVh6WJQgCP7y9bYif-Cdk70pWr4Vi7pRuPqHHP6O3vQPmE0bfe6tfbrLflRD2kWHyFWIjWCJyTwB5tOYDZoR_8/n38DwM7uwy3azqY9ti5Av55Fz9fe4-5K/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着注意力转向人道主义危机，委内瑞拉人搜寻更多地震废墟"&gt;造成至少 1,700 人死亡&lt;/a&gt;。现在，随着国家努力复苏，其经济前景开始显得黯淡。由于投资者考虑到&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/lW7keB8O6rZeK5FtRQDjB5dzk9P1pFY7XMRHI_SbdzncZMC_kryQ3fLCwjjko6d6phEm7jaLDVi4h8fkMZ7DO6z_Xi5hZgPJNMvagCDV4n4wnbv9sgmJtqWeXyRsmTy_UPh95JVDr_Gng5Tto5W1MKy_XPhtOoPhcIz41z47EuD-nuLYjZLclhS_xKHD1F_qmJmWQUMDfxmVy63gLNVF4wyAx7Y1wqNQEEy9K6xhsOqJ_8dQmfjJK4PErA1FY3XcXAMtefKacVjQb9Fhn9TtafzCkIVA47tP4yOj__zYRH66OF3I-zPDcZzzfMSwCJatMbegZa7lVFtla8TBfxMX_89d7AR_Xf7s5FkER9yd8jhNWENLdXIoNXF8SZx5qjBRpX4vNfCBF00V7g29NMLj0sPoIDWoxu62xA0Vb4T6hrrmbJnA8zRXB74X-G7HCWvA5LN16aYpa8hamFXfyJC6tLj-ItdIOSae9w8PjiP4Mv4VEKobCw94IoRpn_5yZWmoilop6aI6JHAKNoy7kP64hhhsMYXsmls/1aEVdATLHa7FXdlqR3hlTdnpE7azKKYe/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="投资者认为前景黯淡，委内瑞拉债券涨势消退"&gt;更加黯淡的财务前景&lt;/a&gt;，债券价格暴跌，这加剧了全面债务重组的挑战。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;当救援人员寻找&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/7IazaDq8lUWYvM_p5aBZeoZey5qBLL2rdb11sCBdtCo3eSdeE0CdJLB17aOS0jzI2sF0Bwhub9_t_AWGA6_Ujyv42f